{"tid":1099324,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打男朋友都係咁","createTime":"2019-04-09T17:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T15:41:50.000Z","uid":210635,"like":10,"dislike":91,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"dc3c1145d8ee2eaddc69810e4e4d9adf390bdee8","tid":1099324,"uid":210635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:01:44.000Z","msg":"知佢第二日要返工叫佢早啲訓<br />\n佢口口聲聲話去訓教但其實冇訓係度玩手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實唔係唔比你遲訓<br />\n只係唔想你返工冇精神姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你唔洗返工嘅我理撚得你幾點訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實你同我講遲少少訓我都冇咁唔開心<br />\n但你依家係呃尻我喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我比啲ex搞到成個人都好冇安全感同好易亂諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係咪應該對佢隻眼開隻眼閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb502c70a8a4b580f6aafc5f8cd9b874bb3d4bb","tid":1099324,"uid":142758,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:04:27.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dea1f2fb521d02a2e7270fb3091853af832ca7d","tid":1099324,"uid":225768,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:06:18.000Z","msg":"冇乜自制力咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重點係呃你其實未訓住"},{"pid":"b2b3993b985803da828c40f6887ae252eac308a3","tid":1099324,"uid":88689,"like":31,"dislike":3,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:07:31.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係因為你冇俾到足夠空間佢做自己喜歡既野<br />\n佢迫住要犧牲埋自己訓覺同休息既時間去打機"},{"pid":"151d9ef7f32ae3d9f73aa6f261d039a7c23c27d5","tid":1099324,"uid":247362,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:08:13.000Z","msg":"我自己個人都係咁 叫我訓 我都會玩陣電話先訓<br />\n我會由佢 又唔係做啲咩 咁佢第二日返工無精神係佢既事<br />\n咁大個人識平衡 雙方即使講早抖 我都會講句<br />\n玩多陣電話好訓啦"},{"pid":"e3ff6a7771b9ce9dcb3f8132bc6c6d1059f8a0ea","tid":1099324,"uid":211081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:09:41.000Z","msg":"咁小事都唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763d090e01a22d5d9d74a29387d030abc2099b97","tid":1099324,"uid":89105,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"話訓教 其實玩電話 已經平常到好似定律咁<br />\n就算呢個係一個大話 都已經變到好似理所當然咁<br />\n因為你知道 一個人臨訓前 就算同自己講要訓教<br />\n但隻手唔知點解好難唔㩒多幾下電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n結論係  睇化啲啦 玩電話有癮架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db9a094b529fbd27874144c2318f2fb8f4c1863","tid":1099324,"uid":210635,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b2b3993b985803da828c40f6887ae252eac308a3","tid":1099324,"uid":88689,"like":31,"dislike":3,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:07:31.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係因為你冇俾到足夠空間佢做自己喜歡既野<br />\n佢迫住要犧牲埋自己訓覺同休息既時間去打機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:14:02.000Z","msg":"我平時都冇乜點管佢<br />\n佢自己都好少打機<br />\n但我只係唔中意佢咁樣呃我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5711f7fbf5f63ae18dfe4f843633f10d2c40d2","tid":1099324,"uid":210635,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"e3ff6a7771b9ce9dcb3f8132bc6c6d1059f8a0ea","tid":1099324,"uid":211081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:09:41.000Z","msg":"咁小事都唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:14:53.000Z","msg":"唔中意比人呃嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2acc704df6b598674675a62f8c0b8c27355b52a3","tid":1099324,"uid":210635,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"4dea1f2fb521d02a2e7270fb3091853af832ca7d","tid":1099324,"uid":225768,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:06:18.000Z","msg":"冇乜自制力咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重點係呃你其實未訓住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:16:34.000Z","msg":"咁樣會搞到我成日形住佢有其他野都呃緊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0757bb297fa06aa50ecaecb89d384d9847eba2","tid":1099324,"uid":24854,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:26:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5c37a056eb26ecc5a4ccc1b7af5bcc6220d7939","tid":1099324,"uid":215160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"同你一樣 每次同我講完訓教都發現佢仲用緊電話<br />\n我都會好唔開心覺得好似俾人呃咁<br />\n但可能佢真係去訓但訓唔著先玩下唔好咁介意啦<br />\n<br />\n我係咁同自己講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3419cdbda036224ce7641da5887322295cfd449e","tid":1099324,"uid":243290,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b66d66ce83b1df07caca1b5afef177ddc92e1e","tid":1099324,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:38:33.000Z","msg":"玩一陣姐 大把人係咁"},{"pid":"f1514e842f66cefb3fe31a8662944b2c0322ad52","tid":1099324,"uid":210635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5c37a056eb26ecc5a4ccc1b7af5bcc6220d7939","tid":1099324,"uid":215160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"同你一樣 每次同我講完訓教都發現佢仲用緊電話<br />\n我都會好唔開心覺得好似俾人呃咁<br />\n但可能佢真係去訓但訓唔著先玩下唔好咁介意啦<br />\n<br />\n我係咁同自己講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:45:27.000Z","msg":"等我都做下心理建設先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望佢真係訓唔著先玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7399bcf77a2db988282dc404797c4fef36936009","tid":1099324,"uid":210635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3419cdbda036224ce7641da5887322295cfd449e","tid":1099324,"uid":243290,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:36:55.000Z","msg":"<